# Changelog

All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

The format is based on [Keep a Changelog](https://keepachangelog.com/en/1.0.0/),
and this project adheres to [Semantic Versioning](https://semver.org/spec/v2.0.0.html).

## [Unreleased]

### Added
- Initial project setup with Next.js 15/16 and TypeScript
- Bold yet playful typography system (Space Grotesk, Inter, JetBrains Mono)
- Extended J.A.R.V.I.S. color palette with playful accents (coral, lavender, teal)
- Holographic design tokens (colors, spacing, type scale, gradients)
- PPR with conditional rendering for adaptive WebGL/CSS-only experiences
- Device detection utilities (mobile, WebGL support, hardware capability)
- Performance monitoring (frame time tracking, particle auto-disable, memory budgeting)
- Zod schema validation for blog post frontmatter
- Shader components (Scanlines, Particles) with custom GLSL
- HolographicCard component with 3D tilt effect
- Dual-path Hero section (Quick Pitch modal, Deep Dive scroll)
- Unit tests for utilities (deviceDetection, performance, blogSchema)
- ESLint and Prettier configuration
- Tailwind CSS with custom holographic theme

### Changed
- Upgraded from React 19 to React 18 for R3F compatibility
- Downgraded @testing-library/react to v14 for React 18 compatibility

